	<exercise><statement><p> Does the mass of displaced water depend on the mass of the totally submerged object or on the volume of the submerged object? </p></statement></exercise>
	<exercise><statement><p> There are two identical cargo ships.  One has a cargo of 5 tons of steel and the other has a cargo of 5 tons of styrofoam.  Which ship floats lower in the water? </p></statement></exercise>
