	<li><p> We would like the water to be at some cool, stable, and uniform temperature.  Can you imagine what convenient temperature we can maintain for the water which satisfies these three conditions?  HINT: The container for the water must also be in thermal equilibrium with the water before the unknown metal is added.</p></li>
</ol></p>
