<subsection><title>Defining Your Terms</title>

<p>As a group, take one of the three lenses and your white screen into a dark room so that you can see a brighter room through a doorway.  Have one person in the group go stand in the bright room and move around while another person looks through the lens.  Then trade places until everybody has a chance to look through the lens.</p>

<exercise>
<statement><p>
<ol>
